room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Island" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: We did the Jurassic Island Escape Room and it was super fun! The room was very well themed and decorated. My only complaint when comparing to other escape rooms is that the story was not very apparent. There were tons of clues around the room on laminated papers because the story really didn't make much sense. I wish it would have been more well thought out because all the technology in the room is the best I've ever seen in an escape room. I would still recommend this place to friends.

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Island" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: I dont see any reviews for the Jurassic island room so here is one....it was amazing, my kid and I solved it with a few seconds left and we were both very pleased with the whole operation...we are going back to do wizard theme tomorrow.
